  <summary date="2021-07-21T18:37:41Z" status="Introduced in House">Hazardous Duty Pay for Frontline Federal Workers Act

This bill temporarily entitles federal employees, including certain employees of the Veterans Health Administration and the Transportation Security Administration, who are exposed to COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) during duty to a pay differential, as set by the Office of Personnel Management.</summary>
